result.name: Kwong Yuen Estate

reviews.text: The estate carpark is not easy to get in and out. skillful drivers only.
Nice place to have a walk.
A well planned community with an adequate wet market.  A lot of eateries, restaurants, take outs. The best is a bus terminus that provides diverse bus routes.

An estate built on the hill 27 years ago which had won an architecture award before! A lot of trees and flowers were planted giving you the feeling of natural. There is a fountain as well, but nowadays it's not filled with water for most of the year. It would be pleasant living there still!
There are 2 supermarkets, 4 convenient stores and 1 wet market in the area. Sufficient for residents' needs on daily meals and fulfill their necessities.
If you do not want to cook, there are more than 5 restaurants for you to choose. From fast food to big restaurant, asian foods to western foods, you could always pick what would feed your appetite.
In the estate aspect, there is 1 kindergarten, 1 primary school instated, while 1 middle school is near for only 5 minutes walk. Sports facilities are not missed neither. Soccer field and basketball field could also be found. There is even a community center and a post office in the estate, which are not easily found in every other estates nowadays.
The only issue needs to be concerned is the transportation. Since it is on a hill, there would only be bus as the public transport. But still, the bus lines are quite widely spread. You could get to the down town and change another bus or transports to your final destination. Luckily, Hong Kong is not too big... Cheers!
The new food court open till 2:00am

result.name: 大快活

reviews.text: 進駐一般舊式屋邨的集團快餐店，管理層都懂得安排適當的服務員人手;因此這裏大部分的服務員都是上了年紀的人士，無擬服務態度是較一般年青人較佳，但遇上人客爆滿的時刻，其工作效率就未必能應付得來！所以這處午飯時段，要有足夠的忍耐力才能夠享用一頓美食。
員工有禮，平日下午茶人較小，從玻璃窗看街景挺舒服的。
這間分店環境比較寬敞，相片吸引，但真實食物與相片略有不符，味道尚可，分量充足，紅豆冰雞髀絕配好味！
員工服務、食物水準和管理層都值得一讚!
廣源邨大快活🆗,地方好,冷氣適中
